{"tid":1425590,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[夏季大三角]七夕拍拖、追女溝仔無新意？聽晚去觀星啦！","createTime":"2019-08-06T18:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T08:41:01.000Z","uid":265288,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bbc3ebaaa48cafb3a4055f0e8d3ab92b6a630ea6","tid":1425590,"uid":265288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:54:05.000Z","msg":"時正七夕 <br />\n機會黎啦飛雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話觀星好悶不了？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n七夕睇夏季大三角先係最浪漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n夏季大三角係咩黎呢？<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hokoon.edu.hk/weeklysp/images/1506_5L1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hokoon.edu.hk%2Fweeklysp%2Fimages%2F1506_5L1.jpg&h=0812d0f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n夏季三大角係由牛郎星、織女星同天津四組成<br />\n牛郎同織女大家都好熟啦<br />\n<br />\n咁天津星係咩黎呢<br />\n其實就係<strong>喜鵲橋</strong>啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁香港有咩地方好觀星呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">太空館</span></strong>啦  仲有得學觀星喎 一舉兩得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n祝拍緊拖嘅各位恩恩愛愛<br />\n單身嘅靠今次呢條喜鵲橋追到意中人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f18ff5990245ac5a462eebcaf542d48f13fcb1d","tid":1425590,"uid":218575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:55:21.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗帶定觀星筆"},{"pid":"45e5d8adc71c5dd9ccf7203c0d561b4a84500e5f","tid":1425590,"uid":265288,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9f18ff5990245ac5a462eebcaf542d48f13fcb1d","tid":1425590,"uid":218575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:55:21.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗帶定觀星筆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:57:19.000Z","msg":"最好自備啦<br />\n到時可能現場太多人學觀星<br />\n會唔夠派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a58dc5ce0c6eb460b9c6a698ff37e6182078a0eb","tid":1425590,"uid":66208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:05:25.000Z","msg":"觀星？唔洗用套嘅！用筆就得！"},{"pid":"ab0b6f13722522bedcfbafc94e9a4f9dc9a4a1ff","tid":1425590,"uid":102185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:07:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f8f937cb7633a852fa5f48fec503eef7085694","tid":1425590,"uid":265288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a58dc5ce0c6eb460b9c6a698ff37e6182078a0eb","tid":1425590,"uid":66208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:05:25.000Z","msg":"觀星？唔洗用套嘅！用筆就得！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:15:02.000Z","msg":"個套用黎保護支筆都得掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n觀星用嘅唔平架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05154bc3c561a30265e43796013eabc1fc832d79","tid":1425590,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c3d02ce807df5bfaa6d52ead78551ac89bd53a","tid":1425590,"uid":265288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05154bc3c561a30265e43796013eabc1fc832d79","tid":1425590,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:20:42.000Z","msg":